OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772154219
OL,3,CSpain to check passports of Brits
OL,4,Carriving in Gibraltar under post-
OL,5,CBrexit deal
OL,7,FBrits travelling to Gibraltar will
OL,8,Fhave their passports checked by
OL,9,FSpanish officials as well as officials
OL,10,Ffrom Gibraltar under a new post-Brexit
OL,11,Fagreement.
OL,13,FThe changes mean those flying into the
OL,14,FBritish overseas territory will face
OL,15,Fdual border checks, while the deal has
OL,16,Freduced checks at the land border with
OL,17,FSpain.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
