OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772154219
OL,3,CSpain to check passports of Brits
OL,4,Carriving in Gibraltar under post-
OL,5,CBrexit deal
OL,7,FThe 15,000 people who cross the border
OL,8,Fwith Spain every day will now be able
OL,9,Fto travel freely between the two
OL,10,Fterritories under the draft treaty
OL,11,Fagreed by the UK, the EU, and the
OL,12,Fgovernment of Gibraltar.
OL,14,FThe deal outlines arrangements for a
OL,15,F"fluid border" for both people and
OL,16,Fgoods, with a tailored customs model
OL,17,Fto "eliminate burdensome goods
OL,18,Fchecks", according to the UK
OL,19,Fgovernment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772154219
OL,3,CSpain to check passports of Brits
OL,4,Carriving in Gibraltar under post-
OL,5,CBrexit deal
OL,7,FIt is hoped the deal will settle the
OL,8,Funcertainty about the governance of
OL,9,Fthe Gibraltar-Spain border after the
OL,10,FBrexit vote in 2016.
OL,12,FThe draft agreement does not affect
OL,13,Fsovereignty, stating that nothing
OL,14,Fsigned "shall constitute the basis for
OL,15,Fany assertion or denial of
OL,16,Fsovereignty" over the Rock, and
OL,17,Fprotects UK autonomy of key military
OL,18,Ffacilities.
OL,26,@vD@HOUxD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
