OL,3,CSpain to check passports of Brits
OL,4,Carriving in Gibraltar under post-
OL,5,CBrexit deal
OL,7,FGibraltar's airport is run by the
OL,8,FMinistry of Defence and hosts an RAF
OL,9,Fbase. The overseas territory also has
OL,10,Fan important naval facility.
OL,12,FChief Minister of Gibraltar, Fabian
OL,13,FPicardo, said the treaty protects the
OL,14,F"British way of life" on the Rock,
OL,15,Fwhile "unlocking new opportunities for
OL,16,Fgrowth and prosperity".
OL,18,FThe treaty, published in draft form on
OL,19,FThursday, still needs to be signed,
OL,20,Fratified, and implemented.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@UO]wD@GOUxD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
