OL,3,CSpain to check passports of Brits
OL,4,Carriving in Gibraltar under post-
OL,5,CBrexit deal
OL,7,FForeign Office minister Stephen
OL,8,FDoughty said: "This treaty ensures
OL,9,Fthat Gibraltar's economy, people, and
OL,10,Ffuture are protected as an integral
OL,11,Fpart of the British family.
OL,13,F"Working closely with the Government
OL,14,Fof Gibraltar ` and agreeing nothing
OL,15,Fwithout their consent ` we have a
OL,16,Ftreaty that preserves sovereignty and
OL,17,Fdelivers certainty when Gibraltar's
OL,18,Fway of life was threatened. "
OL,26,@pD@OOUuD@AOU
