OL,4,Carriving in Gibraltar under post-
OL,5,CBrexit deal
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FShadow Foreign Office minister Wendy
OL,13,FMorton warned the government against
OL,14,Fhanding Spain "new powers over entry,
OL,15,Fresidency, infrastructure and
OL,16,Fenforcement."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
