CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772154219
OL,3,CSpain to check passports of Brits
OL,4,Carriving in Gibraltar under post-
OL,5,CBrexit deal
OL,7,F"This is a treaty of over a thousand
OL,8,Fpages with profound constitutional
OL,9,Fchanges that fundamentally reshapes
OL,10,Fhow Gibraltar's border, airport and
OL,11,Flegal framework will operate, yet
OL,12,FParliament has not seen a single page
OL,13,Fof it," she said.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
