PN,31508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772154219
OL,3,CSpain to check passports of Brits
OL,4,Carriving in Gibraltar under post-
OL,5,CBrexit deal
OL,7,F"Gibraltar is British. Its people have
OL,8,Frepeatedly and overwhelmingly chosen
OL,9,Fto remain under British sovereignty.
OL,10,FAny treaty that hands Spain new powers
OL,11,Fover entry, residency, infrastructure
OL,12,For enforcement must be examined line
OL,13,Fby line by Parliament before it takes
OL,14,Feffect.
OL,16,F"Parliament cannot be expected to sign
OL,17,Fa blank cheque to the EU. We need the
OL,18,Ffull treaty in front of us before a
OL,19,Fsingle provision is allowed to take
OL,20,Feffect."
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU|D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
