CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772154219
OL,3,CSpain to check passports of Brits
OL,4,Carriving in Gibraltar under post-
OL,5,CBrexit deal
OL,7,FGibraltar was ceded to the UK by Spain
OL,8,Funder the Treaty of Utrecht in 1713,
OL,9,Fand the population is heavily in
OL,10,Ffavour of remaining a British overseas
OL,11,Fterritory.
OL,13,FThe last time it voted on a proposal
OL,14,Fto share sovereignty with Spain, in
OL,15,F2002, almost 99% of Gibraltarians
OL,16,Frejected the move.
OL,18,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,19,FPolitics? Tom and Robert dig into the
OL,20,Fbiggest issues dominating the
OL,21,Fpolitical agenda in every episode...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
